<p><strong></strong>The 12 Sprints of Becoming a Software Developer are about to conclude. As we turn the page on another calendar year, what would you like to learn in 2022 in order to advance your career? Simply visit <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53267065">Post Pandemic Challenge &gt; Getting Started</a></strong> and click <strong>"Add a reply"</strong> to enter your wish list for Santa's review.</p>
<p><strong>Narrowing the skills gap, one chapter at a time.</strong></p>
