<p><strong>December Sprint #2</strong></p>
<p><strong></strong>The current sprint began <strong>Thursday, December 16</strong> and concludes <strong>Friday, December 31</strong>. The <strong>Post Pandemic Challenge</strong> will end on the final day of this year. After that date, Microsoft will no longer offer these courses for free and will resume a charge of $30 per month to access its LinkedIn Learning library.</p>
<p>If you are ready to take the final sprint, simply review <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53267065">Post Pandemic Challenge &gt; Getting Started</a>.</strong> Then, post an Introduction stating what you will commit to work on during this final two-week sprint. You can also post any barriers you might be encountering in shifting into post pandemic gear in the comments under <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53267065">Post Pandemic Challenge &gt; Getting Started</a></strong>.</p>
